{"tid":2437340,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–腸沾黏","createTime":"2021-03-07T22:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T17:03:41.000Z","uid":38861,"like":60,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1c1f2da02cf62e1b91f7be550bd21f89c745a2b7","tid":2437340,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T22:01:12.000Z","msg":"腸道手術過後，病人的腸道手術位置有機會與鄰近的腸道連結出一層新的組織，此現象名為沾黏(Adhesion)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O6yUpgc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO6yUpgc.png&h=b8b7c99d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這些組織有機會阻塞腸道或釀成腹痛，需要再進行額外的手術剷除它們。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）當腹腔腸道出現傷口時，我們的免疫細胞便會前往傷處協助傷口收復工作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eyDUpge.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeyDUpge.png&h=71f0112d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而手術沾黏的形成，相信是因為手術時所做成的傷口過大，激發某部份的免疫細胞為了修復傷口而所組成的不良產物。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）從圖中可見，短短30分鐘便有無數多的免疫細胞前來聚集傷口處。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YvKcVnX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYvKcVnX.png&h=95c08ccf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近科學家們找出了負責這過程的免疫細胞品種，並發現這些免疫細胞是依靠著表面其中一種蛋白質互相連結對方。<br />\n<br />\n若果能建立安全的手段短暫性破壞這些蛋白質的互動，將會能夠大大減低手術後所出現的組織沾黏不良效果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058jH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=322f97f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058jH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=762bd68e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.gastrosurgery.co.uk/intestinal-adhesions-treatment-london/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gastrosurgery.co.uk%2Fintestinal-adhesions-treatment-london%2F&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058jH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=f2544257\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gastrosurgery.co.uk/intestinal-adhesions-treatment-london/</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://science.sciencemag.org/content/371/6533/eabe0595\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscience.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2F371%2F6533%2Feabe0595&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058jH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=a0fb4897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://science.sciencemag.org/content/371/6533/eabe0595</a>"},{"pid":"80bff53d7a72b6ce0bb8dbece1748e74f5d5bd90","tid":2437340,"uid":172172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T22:05:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaac985cb8469378fc39dc11562caa7a4c93170c","tid":2437340,"uid":33728,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T22:08:48.000Z","msg":"有用的資料"},{"pid":"bc0f47389850a2d579a76f434a9e7c5b7a137895","tid":2437340,"uid":78349,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T22:13:14.000Z","msg":"熊仔餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ff75fb123ab8fd3b2b2bb9eba214be74465257